close_reason: capture_level enforcement implemented and verified with unit regressions
body: The capture_level field exists in settings.telemetry but is only copied into the command_start payload. No code branches on minimal/redacted/max to actually reduce data collection. This means the setting is misleading - users who set capture_level to minimal still have full data collected.
